  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Setup obrigatório\n\n**Credencial Supabase API**\nSettings > Credentials > Add > Supabase API\n- Host: https://oezifbbcnqfpjakyrohh.supabase.co\n- Service Role Secret: sua service_role key\n\nVincule nos nós:\n- Download CSV do Storage\n- Upsert no Supabase\n\n**Payload do webhook (POST):**\n{\n  file_path: <caminho no bucket, ex: uuid/empresa/arquivo.csv>,\n  table: minha_tabela,\n  on_conflict: id\n}",
        "height": 340,
        "width": 500,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "4c864c1e-cdcf-489c-9b70-947c636e22cf",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        0,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "csv-upsert",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "c5ce36ff-c7e1-49df-b85c-085ecda4fa34",
      "name": "Webhook Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        0,
        400
      ],
      "webhookId": "csv-upsert-webhook"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "f2",
              "name": "file_path",
